        "\n",
        "I attended the [R/Pharma](https://rinpharma.com/) virtual conference for the first time ([2025](https://rinpharma.com/docs/RPH2025/)). The conference is focused on the use of R in pharma, encouraging open-source and cross-company collaboration. \n",
        "The following section highlights summarises some of the workshops and talks, condensed to their key takeaways. This serves mainly as a repository for links to presentations and workshop materials.\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "::::::\n",
